Subject: Love Hacked? 36 Questions That May Change Your Life
Description: Can there be a formula to the way our feelings grow for each other? Some say a series of 36 questions can create emotional intimacy in a very short period of time, even among strangers. Come and join our experiment to see such claims hold true! Due to the nature of the activity, attendance will be limited.  Participation will depend on demographically matching partner availability.  Couples encouraged if space allows.  This panel is for ages 18+ only. Minors are not allowed (with or without a parent).  Speakers include:Edward Fleece - Track: After Dark  - Duration: 1 hour and 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
